DRUG DEVELOPMENT
Conclusion: Post-hoc analysis based on pooled data from three double-blinded CVOTs
suggests, albeit with a low number of events, a reduced risk of dementia with liraglutide
or semaglutide treatment in patients with type 2 diabetes.
